MetriDoc uses the web framework [Grails|http://www.grails.org].  Grails is similar to the web framework ruby on rails framework,
but sits on top of the Groovy language.  Anyone with Java web experience, or experience in rapid development
environments such as Rails or Django should pick up Grails quickly.

Here are some Grails resources:

* [Grails Website|http://www.grails.org]
* [Free OFPS Oreily online book|http://ofps.oreilly.com/titles/9781449323936/index.html]
* [Grails User Manual|http://grails.org/doc/latest/]
* [Tutorials|http://grails.org/Tutorials]
* [Grails in Action|http://www.manning.com/gsmith/]



